{"tid":407161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒系列] 司機假結婚後始知中介是女兒男友 官：真係咁啱得咁蹺","createTime":"2017-09-20T08:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T12:59:20.000Z","uid":77196,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8a9662d1fdbdd34de70f0fbef13bdeef55c4eb","tid":407161,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"六旬的士司機經中介人介紹下，與一名港人的61歲內地情婦假結婚，協助對方獲得居港權，收酬1,000元，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>事後才知中介人是女兒的同居男友。女兒其後為中介人誕下兩名子女，中介人頓成司機的「哎吔女婿」。惟中介人終跟女友分手，司機疑不滿哎吔女婿不負責任、始亂終棄，決定「攬炒」自首，做「金手指」大義滅親，最終他被判囚8個月，哎吔女婿則囚18個月</strong></span>。哎吔女婿不服上訴，今遭駁回。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人寵物美容師何新榮（37歲）一方指，原審裁判官不應考慮第一控方證人、即何的同居女友父親薛鎮南（60歲）的證供，因薛既與上訴人相識，亦是共犯，有份參與假結婚交易。上訴一方亦質疑薛起初稱「等錢使」，透過一名的士司機認識上訴人，希望可假結婚賺快錢，惟後來又稱到律師樓完成所有手續後，才知上訴人是女兒男友，並與上訴人認識，認為兩種說法前後矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n  律政司一方反駁指，原審裁判官已於判詞表明薛的說法有不盡不實之處，但並非案中關鍵，而上訴人亦從沒否認自己曾於涉案律師樓出現，明顯是進行假結婚。法官亦估計的士司機介紹薛進行假結婚時，並不知道中介人是薛女的男友，直言「真係咁啱得咁蹺」。"},{"pid":"29c654c37ea4ce30d09cf20745d08b07e79637da","tid":407161,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170920/57233471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170920%2F57233471&d=O4zg5sAizOM5IVs%2B7QnJGr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=95f189d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170920%2F57233471&h=f24b1fcf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170920/57233471</a>"},{"pid":"1b65deb967ab67f206a7e457fcf31304df8e6c08","tid":407161,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"為一千蚊坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c50ce673dfc2dea5c5394912b43f37f5493ba7","tid":407161,"uid":116131,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為一千蚊坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔甘心個女比個男人始亂終棄"},{"pid":"50b212d2f3b64958e5169bcff735564f9bd34a91","tid":407161,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"6...61歲內地情婦&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e63d7d2f3d5a87b8126c55dbd7ed9add89f0401a","tid":407161,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">協助對方獲得居港權，收酬1,000元</span><br />\n<br />\n呢件廢老為咗一千蚊賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e818c7c44dcc7353b08ddbe74c650932e9829fd","tid":407161,"uid":45650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"為果1000蚊, D廢鬼真係唔死都無用"},{"pid":"a766012cee1b12c61b270099c2f8b41806245dc8","tid":407161,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為一千蚊坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔甘心個女比個男人始亂終棄</blockquote><br />\n一個好爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c8a21e895d6602255c8f14a0a7dcf9c542133b","tid":407161,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6...61歲內地情婦&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n見你個reply特碌返上去睇🙄"},{"pid":"f38d7dc88609e70aa49f08c85cdc8ec9f8696016","tid":407161,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"假結婚只收一千蚊酬勞？"},{"pid":"9b439bb5ccb6747859c1a9f64713a15ddbcdb4b6","tid":407161,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假結婚只收一千蚊酬勞？</blockquote><br />\n通常報細數搏判少d"},{"pid":"b4daef27d5bb47695a2aeb3ef6512417e503d4e7","tid":407161,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"生左兩個先唔要 .. 咁撚仆街"},{